KeysToEntries.story_5_2_000:
Fast… you’re even more
skilled than I’d heard…‼
KeysToEntries.story_5_2_001:
But… making the car run well
is the only thing
I’m good at…‼
KeysToEntries.story_5_2_002: That’s why… I can’t lose here…‼
KeysToEntries.story_5_2_003:
I’ve made up my mind…
I’m joining Project D.
KeysToEntries.story_5_2_004:
I’ll claim the spot
at the top of it all…‼
